snippet.title: Backrooms Rec. ( Game ) ( Found Footage ) Trailer | UE5 | Steam | Pre-Access Launch
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2275020/Backrooms_Rec/

Introducing the chilling world of the Backrooms, where nightmares lurk and reality fades away. Immerse yourself in the eerie corridors and unravel the hidden secrets of this solo-developed horror game. The Steam page is now live! Visit the link in the description to embark on this terrifying journey.
